final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Align the agent on the horizontal axis (y=10) by moving DOWN. Because the agent is at y=8, it must move DOWN 10 - 8 = 2 times. Next, move to pick up the Key (x=13, y=8). Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Pick up the Key by moving into its space and become purple. Then, move to reach the cyan object (x=18, y=8) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is now at x=13, it must move RIGHT 18 - 13 = 5 times. Open the cyan KeyDoor by moving onto it, which will destroy the Key. Finally, move to reach the goal (x=19, y=10) by moving RIGHT and then UP. Because the agent is now at x=18, it must move RIGHT 1 time and then UP 2 times.
